== George Cross Foundation ==
The Royal Ulster Constabulary GC Foundation was established by virtue of the Police (Northern Ireland) Act 2000 for the purpose of &quot;marking the sacrifice and honouring the achievements of the Royal Ulster Constabulary&quot;.

